@startuml "Ionosense HPC - Research Platform Overview"
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam rectangleBackgroundColor #F0F8FF
skinparam rectangleBorderColor #4169E1
skinparam roundCorner 15
skinparam arrowColor #4169E1
skinparam arrowThickness 2
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #E8F5E9
skinparam noteBorderColor #4CAF50
skinparam packageBackgroundColor #E6F3FF
skinparam packageBorderColor #4169E1

title Ionosense HPC - High-Performance Research Platform for Ionospheric Signal Analysis
footer © 2025 - Next-Generation Signal Processing Infrastructure

' ============================================================================
' Research Applications
' ============================================================================
package "**RESEARCH APPLICATIONS**" <<Research>> #E8F5E9 {
  
  rectangle "**Ionospheric Scintillation Analysis**" as IonosphereApp #FFFFFF
  note right of IonosphereApp
    * Equatorial plasma bubbles
    * Polar cap patches  
    * TEC variations
    * Phase/amplitude scintillation
    * Multi-scale phenomena
  end note
  
  rectangle "**Real-Time Signal Monitoring**" as RealtimeApp #FFFFFF
  note right of RealtimeApp
    * <100μs latency achievable
    * Continuous streaming
    * Deadline compliance >99%
    * Live anomaly detection
  end note
  
  rectangle "**High-Throughput Processing**" as ThroughputApp #FFFFFF
  note right of ThroughputApp
    * >10,000 FPS capability
    * 25 GB/s data throughput
    * Batch processing optimization
    * Scalable to large datasets
  end note
}

' ============================================================================
' Core Platform
' ============================================================================
package "**IONOSENSE HPC PLATFORM**" <<Platform>> #E6F3FF {
  
  together {
    rectangle "**GPU-Accelerated\nExecutor Architecture**" as Engine #FFE4B5
    note bottom of Engine
      **Performance Achievements (v0.9.4+):**
      * BatchExecutor: 86.79 µs (high-throughput)
      * StreamingExecutor: 122.25 µs (low-latency)
      * 100-1000× faster than CPU
      * Real-time capable
      * Energy efficient
      * Production ready
    end note
    
    rectangle "**Intelligent\nExperiment Orchestration**" as Orchestration #F0F8FF
    note bottom of Orchestration
      **Automation Features:**
      * Parameter optimization
      * Parallel experiments
      * Automatic analysis
      * Report generation
    end note
    
    rectangle "**Reproducible\nResearch Framework**" as Framework #F0F8FF
    note bottom of Framework
      **Research Standards:**
      * Full reproducibility
      * Version control
      * Experiment tracking
      * Collaborative ready
    end note
  }
}

' ============================================================================
' Key Capabilities
' ============================================================================
package "**KEY CAPABILITIES**" <<Capabilities>> #FFFACD {
  
  rectangle "**Adaptive Configuration**\n---\n**3 Ionosphere Modes:**\n* Real-time monitoring\n* High-resolution analysis\n* Long-term observation\n\n**Flexible Parameters:**\n* FFT: 256 - 32768\n* Batch: 1 - 128\n* Overlap: 0 - 95%" as Config
  
  rectangle "**Comprehensive Benchmarking**\n---\n**Performance Metrics:**\n* Latency profiling\n* Throughput analysis\n* Accuracy validation\n* Real-time compliance\n\n**Automatic Optimization:**\n* Parameter tuning\n* Bottleneck detection" as Benchmark
  
  rectangle "**Scientific Visualization**\n---\n**Analysis Outputs:**\n* Publication-ready figures\n* Interactive dashboards\n* Performance heatmaps\n* Scaling curves\n\n**Export Formats:**\n* SVG/PNG graphics\n* HTML reports\n* CSV/HDF5 data" as Visualization
}

' ============================================================================
' Research Workflow
' ============================================================================
package "**RESEARCH WORKFLOW**" <<Workflow>> #FFE6E6 {
  
  rectangle "**1. Define Experiment**\n---\nSelect configuration\nSet parameters\nChoose benchmarks" as Step1
  
  rectangle "**2. Automated Execution**\n---\nParallel processing\nGPU acceleration\nReal-time tracking" as Step2
  
  rectangle "**3. Analysis & Insights**\n---\nStatistical analysis\nVisualization\nReport generation" as Step3
  
  Step1 -right-> Step2 : "Minutes"
  Step2 -right-> Step3 : "Seconds"
}

' ============================================================================
' Impact & Benefits
' ============================================================================
rectangle "**RESEARCH IMPACT**" as Impact #E8F5E9
note left of Impact
  **Accelerated Discovery:**
  * 100× faster experiments
  * Rapid prototyping
  * Quick iterations
  
  **Enhanced Quality:**
  * Rigorous validation
  * Statistical confidence
  * Reproducible results
  
  **Collaboration:**
  * Shareable workflows
  * Tracked experiments
  * Open standards
end note


' ============================================================================
' Technical Foundation (simplified)
' ============================================================================
rectangle "**Technical Foundation (v0.9.4+)**\n---\n**Core Technologies:**\nCUDA 13.0 | cuFFT | C++17 | Python 3.11\n\n**CLI Tools:**\nionoc (C++ dev) | iprof (profiling) | iono dashboard (analysis)\n\n**Research Tools:**\nMLflow | Hydra | Snakemake | Streamlit | DVC\n\n**Stability Features:**\nGPU Clock Locking (CV: 20% → 5-10%)" as TechBase

' ============================================================================
' Relationships
' ============================================================================

' Applications to Platform
IonosphereApp ==> Engine : leverages
RealtimeApp ==> Engine : leverages
ThroughputApp ==> Engine : leverages

' Platform components
Engine <--> Orchestration : integrates
Orchestration <--> Framework : enables
Framework --> Impact : delivers

' Capabilities integration
Config --> Orchestration : configures
Benchmark --> Orchestration : measures
Visualization --> Framework : presents

' Workflow
Step3 --> Impact : contributes to

' Foundation
TechBase -[hidden]up-> Engine

